	  Matthew Lawrence works a full-time programming job in California but continues solo game development as personal enrichment.
	  Matthew received a degree in Computer Science in 2023.
	  Before college, they self-taught themselves game development. The Ludum Dare game jam, for example, was a regular activity for them through high school.
	  Since then, they continue to make small projects every now and then, but mattlawr is primarily working on ENCHAIN for the foreseeable future.
